## Abaice abati tabatala abapeepapo icamba nangu fwaka imbi, elyo nabafyashi baabo kuti bayabakanda icabipisha nganshi
## Kanshi ngabalefwaya kuti babatombamofye amapi nokubeeba uklaleta umunani lyonse ngabaalya umbwali bwa nama ne nkoko ku mwabo
## Lelo chipumbu taleumfwa kufyo abaice balepapaata, ena angilwefye ukupomba icimushanga ge bange, apwisha asonteka elyo umwine abalilapo ukushantako elyo Icinyambalala naco cashantako
## Abaice ku cintinya cakubatwala kuli bakanyangu awe dobola icamba
## Cilya bapwisha ukufokaula Mumamba na Chibale baumfwa insala, bambi balasekasekafye nga bapenene nokulaumfwa amenso yalebabilila nokucepelako
## Ka Wabo kwisatolokela napa mucanga, kalaowa ne nsamfi, kwati kalipa pamenshi uku kalepunda akati: Eco yawamina iyabunseneme! 
## Kamilo nao alamona tukasokopyo twasanguka amasoja, twatampa nokufooleka, apona na mukuseka
## Ukufuma palya ifi fimambaala kubabwekeshamo ku marabou nokuyabateeka pa fishala fya fisooso afiti: Nomba ikaleni apa peene mulebola, kabili mwalitemwa ukwangala mufibole
## Abaice kwikala palya pene, nabalunshi ne mititi fyalabaniina nakufyakufwala, ifi fipondo fyaikala na mwisamba lya muti fyalalya ne fikopo fye sabi fyapokolewele ku baice, uku filefooba ne fimabange  
## Ilyo babalekeleko, panuma yakubashempaulamo na amapi, ekubutukila kuzwii mukoowa
## Tabamonekeele kuli banakulu naba wishikulu, mapaka icungulo, pantu tabelefwaya beshibe icacitiike
## Banakalulu Mumamba balisunguka saana pakumona saana ifyo aba baice bateetawile umusumba wa bwali
## Ne mplipili balelunga mumunani ishalebaba abana mutuminyototi twaabo ngabaya ku cimbusu uno muku aba baice tabailishenyepo nakalya, baleyokawilafye cinshinshi nokula papaula ameenshi nge ngamila shama Arab mu ciswebebe
## Mumaano yabo bena baletontonkanya abati nalimo uku kufunuka kwa aba baice mulandu wakuti tabaliile ubwakasuba 
## Ico tabaishibe cakutila ilya imikusu abaice aba balenoona ngeshakufwintila abali peshilya camba calebomba mumitwe
## Ukufuma palya peene aba baice balungwa kuli ifi fipondo, fyaisangula babwana ba aba baice abasha bafiko, abafwile ukulafituula umutuulo
## Fyaleti lyonse ngabwaila fyayamukulolela pa Chawama Hall pakuti abaice batwale umanani fishete
## Nga ni cai banwene abaice baleya mukutuula umukaate na shuka, fyayamyanga
## Kanshi abafyashi balemonafye abaice pakulya ubwali ku munanibalenunshakofye, baletobelafye umuto, ubwali bulepita
## Abaice calebabipilafye nga banyina bepikile umusaalu nangu umulembwe, ninshi ifipondo tepabukali, ekubapyata nokubafikina amatwi
## Mukwai kuti amatwi yakaba na seee! 
## Leelo icinyambala, Chimpumbu naka Zikati babuukile nge fibansa nangu impefu, tabalefwiita mulembwe kumokwine no musaalu nefilyo fimbi ifyo abanabo tabengakabila ukulya inshita ili yonse
## Kanshi emukutila mumatumba yapa mashati yaba ngweele wabo bonse balishingwilemo amanenekela pakuti abaice pakuletelamo umulembwe tawalepula, mpaka bayafukumuna, bateyako ifinwa, bapwila
## Aya mashati banyina tabaleyamona pakucapa, pantu caleeta ameepusho nobwafya pakashita kamo keene
## Panuma elyo ifi fipondo fyalasoka abaice afita mailo banyina ngatabakepike inama, inkoko, sosikisi nangu isabi kusukulu naku matilimu beena bekanyatanko na luksa, ninshi balungwa
## Ala mukwai mukalaale mwalikalabana, mwakukulila ucampwike
## Aba bakalume, Mumamba, Chibale, Wabo na Kamilo cabakalipa icakuti babapepesha icamba ico tabatalile nokupoosa amaano ku sukulu
## Chipumbu ena alekele isukulu kale, kanshi incite yakwe yalifye kushanta, ukuseeca abantu mumatumba nokulapikimisha utwaice
## Umubiye, cilya twishibe cinyambalala nanguline caleya kusukulu, caleya mukwikalamofye pamulandu wakutiina bawishi abalecilopola umushipi wapa mukoti nga caloofwa
## Aba baice balefilwa ukusosa ifishinka kubafyashi baabo pamulandu wa micitile ya ifi fipondo pantu baletiina ati nga bayafikakaasha ninshi beena baba pa wanted cilabushiku, 
## nokwangala nokubatuma ku mashitoolo ninshi pafiita
## Icibelushi cakonkelepo abeena-Mumamba, Chibale, Kamilo na Wabo baile mukwimba uvuni mumabala yabene ku musebo waaya ku Ndola
## Awe baingila na mwibala lyafyumbu balaimba nakufisoolilo
## Umo fyamenene intumbukila Wabo alepantamofye kuli macense waba wishi uwapamukoti, fyashukuka, banukula
## Awe mukwai baimba ne cilindi emo bashiika ne fyumbu bakoshapo no mulilo, 
## fyalapa nga maboote ne fimuti fya makole balalya na mabungo, 
## uku balekandula no bulimbo bwakwikatilako utooni nokulengula abeene bafyumbu ngabaleisa
## Kuti lilya baninine ku fimuti bamonafye akatalamukila icinyambalala, Chipumbu na Chikasa baleisa ne mbwa kwibala line baalimo
## Awe balapulumuka ku muti nge ntaakuuku ukuti bafulumuke awe ifipondo fyabatiinya afiti ngabapashika imbwa ilebakanda, 
## fyabafwembanya na mu nteneshi sha mashati yabo, balacoomokafye nga bamukolwe bamina inshama
## Ifipondo fyabalonganya elyo fyalabalulwisha nokubapeela umulandu wakwiba uvuni mwibala lyabene, 
## panuma elyo fyabapikimisha nokwimba akalwimbo abati: 
## Uvuni yakwiba tabobula, ngawaubula teeti wikute! 
## Ifyumbu fyasuka fyapya ifipondo ekupikimisha abaice afiti bashiikule
## Ifyumbu fyapiile busaka-busaka icakuti ne ndimi shalasunda
## Leelo cilya bashikula fyonse ifipondo fyabaposelekofye kamo-kamo nokubatonkosha nokubatiinya afiti kuti fyabatwala ku kapokola
## Abaice cabakalipa abati teeti bapelwepofye pa cibe bapibile, bafwile bacitapo cimo pali ubu bunkalwe bwa fibondo
## Ilyo bafumine ku cifwani balungeme kuzwiii ukuya mukoowa pantu kwalikaba saana elyo ne nsala nayo yalibekata
## Ku zwiii baleya mukusamba mu kamana, ka Mufulira
## Bailesangako abanabo nabambi baleipoola pa menshi nga tutombolilo, nakukaba na see ku congo

